{"tid":2346287,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"國際特赦組織斥12港人案審訊不公 憂囚牢中慘遭酷刑","createTime":"2020-12-30T07:04:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T13:33:47.000Z","uid":240362,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"e22eef9c2ef279a4a363e16075f912f1e8806e21","tid":2346287,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:04:51.000Z","msg":"號稱「陽光司法」的中共，以閉門式「秘密審訊」12位涉潛逃港人，在家屬未能旁聽、被捕者未能由家屬委託律師代表下，對10人宣判最高達3年的刑期。國際特赦組織亞太區域主任Yamini Mishra形容，今日的有關判決是在不公平審訊下作出，憂被判刑港青在囚牢中受酷刑對待。<br />\n<br />\nYamini Mishra回應判決時指，12位港人被剝奪選擇自己法律代表、為自己辯護的權利，多位受家屬委託的內地律師代表，也被中國當局恐嚇，要求他們退出這宗案件，並提及外交人員、記者和家屬均無法出席本周一的閉門聆訊。<br />\n<br />\nYamini Mishra直指，今天的判決是在不公平審訊下作出，而這班被判刑的港青將來在中國監獄中，仍可能面對被酷刑或其他虐待，「中國當局再一次向世界展示，抗爭者不會獲得公平審訊。（The Chinese authorities have shown the world once again that political activists will not receive a fair trial.）」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201230/JQXGMJALQVHU5K3FGLC3D33DJU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201230%2FJQXGMJALQVHU5K3FGLC3D33DJU%2F&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSCTbLluyAJ10yBTn0YNn%2FPw%3D&h=7942004e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201230%2FJQXGMJALQVHU5K3FGLC3D33DJU%2F&h=35036c2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201230/JQXGMJALQVHU5K3FGLC3D33DJU/</a>"},{"pid":"3929d1b850ac9e7f9fe7964c822d0ce27c010037","tid":2346287,"uid":14941,"like":7,"dislike":18,"score":-11,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:05:18.000Z","msg":"篤灰果兩個醒"},{"pid":"d7dee1f9254448e47d6089547a6eb3884121f7df","tid":2346287,"uid":183844,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"3929d1b850ac9e7f9fe7964c822d0ce27c010037","tid":2346287,"uid":14941,"like":7,"dislike":18,"score":-11,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:05:18.000Z","msg":"篤灰果兩個醒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:07:16.000Z","msg":"躝啦垃圾"},{"pid":"e6825bc47bf13ac76d6afb134e6565970ba65f86","tid":2346287,"uid":27